title: SIUE Graduate School Showcases Degree Programs at Annual Open House (Southern Illinois University System)
text: ( Source : Southern Illinois University System ) The Southern Illinois University Edwardsville Graduate School encouraged the pursuit of discovery and creativity through a graduate degree at its annual Open House on Wednesday, Oct. 14 .
